  <entry>
    <title>如何建立一个顺手的wsl2开发环境</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/15/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84wsl2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/15/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84wsl2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装wsl2"><a href="#安装wsl2" class="headerlink" title="安装wsl2"></a>安装wsl2</h2><blockquote><p><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/windows/wsl/install">https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/windows/wsl/install</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/386590591">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/386590591</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="迁移wsl2到非系统盘"><a href="#迁移wsl2到非系统盘" class="headerlink" title="迁移wsl2到非系统盘"></a>迁移wsl2到非系统盘</h2><p>使用lxrunoffline</p><pre><code class="hljs">1. https://github.com/DDoSolitary/LxRunOffline/releases2. lxrunoffline list3. lxrunoffline move -n Ubuntu-20.04 -d D:\linux4. lxrunoffline get-dir -n Ubuntu-20.045. ubuntu2004.exe config --default-user root # 设置登录用户为root</code></pre><h2 id="解决路径复制问题"><a href="#解决路径复制问题" class="headerlink" title="解决路径复制问题"></a>解决路径复制问题</h2><pre><code class="hljs">windows路径为 D:\gitlab\xxx ，而对应的wsl2的路径为 /mnt/d/gitlab/xxx,复制路径的时候很麻烦，所以需要一点点帮助。</code></pre><h3 id="xlaunch"><a href="#xlaunch" class="headerlink" title="xlaunch"></a>xlaunch</h3><pre><code class="hljs">这是个小工具，用来支持显示linux桌面以及提供一些windows和linux之间的交互</code></pre><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><pre><code class="hljs">1. https://github.com/ArcticaProject/vcxsrv/releases2. 点击.exe结尾的大的下载包3. 安装</code></pre><h4 id="进入启动目录"><a href="#进入启动目录" class="headerlink" title="进入启动目录"></a>进入启动目录</h4><pre><code class="hljs">1. win + R2. shell:startup</code></pre><h4 id="设置连接"><a href="#设置连接" class="headerlink" title="设置连接"></a>设置连接</h4><p>新建一个文件config.xlaunch，内容如下</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?xml version=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span> encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">XLaunch</span> <span class="hljs-attr">WindowMode</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;MultiWindow&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">ClientMode</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NoClient&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">LocalClient</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;False&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">Display</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-1&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">LocalProgram</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;xcalc&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">RemoteProgram</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;xterm&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">RemotePassword</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">PrivateKey</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">RemoteHost</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">RemoteUser</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">XDMCPHost</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">XDMCPBroadcast</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;False&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">XDMCPIndirect</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;False&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">Clipboard</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;True&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">ClipboardPrimary</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;True&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">ExtraParams</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">Wgl</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;True&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">DisableAC</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;True&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">XDMCPTerminate</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;False&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也可以打开xlaunch把看到的方框都勾上，其他都下一步也行。</p><h3 id="安装Windows-Terminal"><a href="#安装Windows-Terminal" class="headerlink" title="安装Windows Terminal"></a>安装Windows Terminal</h3><p>直接在Microsoft store下载安装就行。<br>傻瓜操作过程：<br>    1. Win + s 打开搜索框<br>    2. 搜索 Microsoft store<br>    3. 搜索框搜索Windows Terminal<br>    4. 安装</p><h3 id="创建一些脚本"><a href="#创建一些脚本" class="headerlink" title="创建一些脚本"></a>创建一些脚本</h3><ol><li><p>创建脚本存放的地方</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"> mkdir -p /opt/scripts<br> cd /opt/scripts<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"> # </span><span class="language-bash">这个是用来让脚本生效的</span><br>echo &#x27;export PATH=$PATH:/opt/scripts&#x27; &gt;&gt; ~/.profile<br>source ~/.profile<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">这样每次打开wsl2会自动生成wsl2服务的ip到hosts里</span><br>echo &#x27;/opt/scripts/wslip.sh&#x27; &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>一些脚本</p><ol><li>path 用来转换window路径与linux路径 <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python3">#! /usr/bin/python3.8<br># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-<br>import os<br>import sys<br><br>if __name__ == &quot;__main__&quot;:<br>    if len(sys.argv)&gt;1:<br>        path = sys.argv[1]<br>    else:<br>        path = os.popen(&#x27;xclip -o&#x27;).read()<br>        if len(path) == 0:<br>            # 这个地方要换成你xlaunch.exe所在的wsl2的地址<br>            os.system(&quot;/mnt/d/software/VcXsrv/xlaunch.exe&quot;)<br>            exit()<br>    splitResult = path.split(&quot;:&quot;)<br>    if len(splitResult) &lt;=1 :<br>        print(path)<br>        exit()<br>    sh_path = &#x27;/&#x27;.join(splitResult[1].split(&#x27;\\&#x27;))  # transform the windows path to linux path<br>    head=&#x27;/mnt/&#x27; + splitResult[0].lower()<br>    print(head + sh_path)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>cdp 直接跳转到复制的windows路径下<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/bin/bash</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> [[ <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$1</span>&quot;</span> ]];<span class="hljs-keyword">then</span><br> target=$(path <span class="hljs-variable">$1</span>)<br> <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$target</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br> target=$(path)<br> <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$target</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">fi</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>wslip.sh 输出wsl2地址到/etc/hosts，这样就可以访问<a href="http://localhost.ubuntu.com/%E6%9D%A5%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AEwsl2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%86">http://localhost.ubuntu.com/来访问wsl2上的服务了</a><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 更简短的 ipaddr=$(ifconfig eth0 | grep &#x27;inet &#x27; | awk &#x27;&#123;print $2&#125;&#x27;)</span><br>ipaddr=$(ifconfig eth0 | grep <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;inet &#x27;</span> | awk <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;print $2&#125;&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -f /mnt/c/Windows/System32/drivers/etc/hosts /tmp/hosts<br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/ubuntu/d&#x27;</span> /tmp/hosts<br>[[ -n `<span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -n 1 /tmp/hosts` ]] &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$ipaddr</span> localhost.ubuntu.com&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /tmp/hosts<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> /tmp/hosts &gt; /mnt/c/Windows/System32/drivers/etc/hosts<br><span class="hljs-built_in">tail</span> -n -1  /mnt/c/Windows/System32/drivers/etc/hosts<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>可能会没有hosts文件的修改权限，右键hosts文件，切换安全tab,点击编辑，为ALL APPLICATION PACKAGES添加修改权限</p></blockquote></li></ol></li><li><p>现在就可以复制一个地址,例如 D:\software\VcXsrv 选中ctrl+C复制。</p></li><li><p>打开wsl2</p><ol><li>输入cdp，你就可以进入这个目录，如果你有的话</li><li>输入path，你就可以获得转换好的地址/mnt/d/software/VcXsrv</li></ol></li></ol><h2 id="关于rz-sz-不装xshell的解决方案"><a href="#关于rz-sz-不装xshell的解决方案" class="headerlink" title="关于rz/sz ,不装xshell的解决方案"></a>关于rz/sz ,不装xshell的解决方案</h2><p>可以使用zssh替代 ssh ，使用 ctrl+ `(这个是1左边的按键)，然后就可以使用rz/sz了</p><ol><li>sudo apt-get install zssh</li><li><a href="https://phenix3443.github.io/notebook/ubuntu/zssh.html">https://phenix3443.github.io/notebook/ubuntu/zssh.html</a></li></ol><p>操作顺序一般为：<br>    1. 连接到目标服务器，进入需要上传的目录 cd /tmp<br>    2. 输入rz ，此时会出现 waiting to receive.**<br>    3. 使用快捷键 ctrl+ ` ，此时会出现 zssh &gt;<br>    4. 进入你要上传文件的目录 cd /mnt/d/software/VcXsrv<br>    5. 输入  sz -be Xcms.txt 就可以上传了</p><h2 id="关于使用docker导致的内网地址无法访问"><a href="#关于使用docker导致的内网地址无法访问" class="headerlink" title="关于使用docker导致的内网地址无法访问"></a>关于使用docker导致的内网地址无法访问</h2><p>一般来说都是由于docker0冲突导致。设置成不会冲突的网段就行<br>vim /etc/docker/daemon.json</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;bip&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;10.55.0.1/16&quot;</span> <br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="国内可用的-docker-源"><a href="#国内可用的-docker-源" class="headerlink" title="国内可用的 docker 源"></a>国内可用的 docker 源</h2><p>vim /etc/docker/daemon.json<br>{<br>  “registry-mirrors”: [<br>    “<a href="https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&quot;/">https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&quot;</a>,<br>    “<a href="https://registry.docker-cn.com&quot;/">https://registry.docker-cn.com&quot;</a>,<br>    “<a href="http://hub-mirror.c.163.com&quot;/">http://hub-mirror.c.163.com&quot;</a><br>  ],<br>}</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
