  <entry>
    <title>hexo建站学习</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/06/hexo%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%99%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/06/hexo%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%99%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="拥有一个linux服务器-带docker的"><a href="#拥有一个linux服务器-带docker的" class="headerlink" title="拥有一个linux服务器,带docker的"></a>拥有一个linux服务器,带docker的</h2><h2 id="安装nodJs"><a href="#安装nodJs" class="headerlink" title="安装nodJs"></a>安装nodJs</h2><h3 id="安装nvm"><a href="#安装nvm" class="headerlink" title="安装nvm"></a>安装nvm</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">https://gitee.com/naozeizei/nvm-for-gitee</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">国内安装nvm比较慢，我写了脚本能快速安装nodejs</span><br>curl -o- https://gitee.com/naozeizei/nvm-for-gitee/raw/master/nvm-cn.sh | bash<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">执行完毕后请重新建立一个terminal</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装nodeJs"><a href="#安装nodeJs" class="headerlink" title="安装nodeJs"></a>安装nodeJs</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">nvm install 12.0.0 # 官网要求6.0至少时12以上，装的时候以官网为准<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h2><ol><li>建议看官网 <a href="http://hexo.io/">http://hexo.io/</a> 完整教程<h3 id="我的执行过程如下"><a href="#我的执行过程如下" class="headerlink" title="我的执行过程如下"></a>我的执行过程如下</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">安装hexo-cli</span><br>npm install hexo-cli -g<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">构建目录</span><br>mkdir /hexo<br>cd /hexo <br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">初始化hexo</span><br>hexo init <br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">npm 初始化</span><br>npm install <br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">生成静态文件，用于展示博客</span><br>hexo g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="安装nginx"><a href="#安装nginx" class="headerlink" title="安装nginx"></a>安装nginx</h2><h3 id="启动docker比较麻烦，还是docker-compose吧"><a href="#启动docker比较麻烦，还是docker-compose吧" class="headerlink" title="启动docker比较麻烦，还是docker-compose吧"></a>启动docker比较麻烦，还是docker-compose吧</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">mkdir /nginx<br>cd /nginx<br>vim docker-compose.yml<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><br><span class="hljs-attr">version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;3.1&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">services:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">nginx:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">nginx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">restart:</span> <span class="hljs-string">always</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">container_name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">nginx</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">environment:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">TZ=Asia/Shanghai</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">ports:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-number">80</span><span class="hljs-string">:80</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-number">443</span><span class="hljs-string">:443</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">./logs:/var/log/nginx</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">/hexo/public:/usr/share/nginx/html</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 冒号前面填hexo/public的路径，其他的不用动</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来就可以直接使用 docker-compose up -d 启动nginx了，使用docker-compose down关闭nginx</p><blockquote><p>以下为docker nginx操作过程</p></blockquote><h3 id="1-拉取最新的nginx镜像"><a href="#1-拉取最新的nginx镜像" class="headerlink" title="1. 拉取最新的nginx镜像"></a>1. 拉取最新的nginx镜像</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">docker pull nginx:latest<br>docker images <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-启动一个临时容器，用来获取默认配置信息"><a href="#2-启动一个临时容器，用来获取默认配置信息" class="headerlink" title="2. 启动一个临时容器，用来获取默认配置信息"></a>2. 启动一个临时容器，用来获取默认配置信息</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">建立nginx目录</span><br>mkdir /nginx<br>cd /nginx<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">启动一个容器</span><br> docker run -d --name nginx nginx<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">查看 容器 获取容器ID 或直接使用名字</span><br>docker container ls<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">在当前目录下创建目录：conf</span> <br>mkdir conf<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">拷贝容器内 Nginx 默认配置文件到本地当前目录下的 conf 目录（<span class="hljs-variable">$PWD</span> 当前全路径）</span><br>docker cp nginx:/etc/nginx/nginx.conf $PWD/conf<br>docker cp nginx:/etc/nginx/conf.d $PWD/conf<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">停止容器</span><br>docker container stop nginx<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">删除容器</span><br>docker container rm nginx<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-启动docker"><a href="#3-启动docker" class="headerlink" title="3. 启动docker"></a>3. 启动docker</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><br>docker run -d -p 80:80  \<br>              -p 443:443  \<br> --name nginxweb \<br> -v /hexo/public:/usr/share/nginx/html \<br> -v /nginx/conf/nginx.conf:/etc/nginx/nginx.conf \<br> -v /nginx/conf/conf.d:/etc/nginx/conf.d \<br> -v /nginx/logs:/var/log/nginx \<br> nginx<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-安装git"><a href="#4-安装git" class="headerlink" title="4. 安装git"></a>4. 安装git</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">yum install git <br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-安装主题"><a href="#5-安装主题" class="headerlink" title="5. 安装主题"></a>5. 安装主题</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">进入主题目录</span><br>cd /hexo/themes/<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">下载fluid</span><br>git clone https://gitee.com/mirrors/hexo-theme-fluid.git<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">重命名</span><br>mv hexo-theme-fluid/ fluid<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>修改 /hexo/_config.yml的 theme <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">fluid</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>添加备案<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">beian:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="7-增加评论功能"><a href="#7-增加评论功能" class="headerlink" title="7. 增加评论功能"></a>7. 增加评论功能</h3><p>这个功能我找了好久，结果发现其实挺简单的.</p><ol><li>我这里使用的是leanCloud，所以先要注册一个leanCloud的账号<ol><li><a href="https://console.leancloud.cn/login">https://console.leancloud.cn/login</a></li><li>登录后点击创建应用</li><li>输入应用名称，选择开发版，点击创建</li><li>现在点击设置（小齿轮）-&gt; 应用凭证 (这个页面开着后面会用)</li></ol></li><li>我们已经安装了fluid主题，进入该主题目录下，编辑_config.yml</li><li>以下操作总结为：<strong>搜索所有的leancloud,把它所在的字段改成leancloud,并且把它上面的enable改成true,web_analytics这个离得特别远，耐心向上找找</strong></li><li>搜索 网页访问统计 或者 <strong>web_analytics</strong>,修改它下面的enable为true。</li><li>搜索 LeanCloud 计数统计 或者 leancloud 填上对应的数据：<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml">    <span class="hljs-comment"># LeanCloud 计数统计，可用于 PV UV 展示，如果 `web_analytics: enable` 没有开启，PV UV 展示只会查询不会增加</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># LeanCloud count statistics, which can be used for PV UV display. If `web_analytics: enable` is false, PV UV display will only query and not increase</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">leancloud:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">app_id:</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#这里写应用凭证AppID</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">app_key:</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#这里写应用凭证AppKey</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">server_url:</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 这里写 REST API 服务器地址 例如： https://ccxctsda4b.lc-cn-n1-shared.com</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">window.location.pathname</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">ignore_local:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>搜索footer<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">footer:</span> <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">statistics:</span><br>   <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>   <span class="hljs-attr">source:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;leancloud&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>搜索 浏览量计数<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 浏览量计数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Number of visits</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">views:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 统计数据来源</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># Data Source</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># Options: busuanzi | leancloud</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">source:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;leancloud&quot;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
